{"tha-ap546:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap546:0.2":"Bhaddiyavagga ","tha-ap546:0.3":"Vangisattheraapadana ","tha-ap546:1.1":"“Padumuttaro nama jino, ","tha-ap546:1.2":"sabbadhammesu cakkhuma; ","tha-ap546:1.3":"Ito satasahassamhi, ","tha-ap546:1.4":"kappe uppajji nayako. ","tha-ap546:2.1":"Yathapi sagare umi, ","tha-ap546:2.2":"gagane viya taraka; ","tha-ap546:2.3":"Evam pavacanam tassa, ","tha-ap546:2.4":"arahantehi cittitam. ","tha-ap546:3.1":"Sadevasuranagehi, ","tha-ap546:3.2":"manujehi purakkhato; ","tha-ap546:3.3":"Samanabrahmanakinne, ","tha-ap546:3.4":"janamajjhe jinuttamo. ","tha-ap546:4.1":"Pabhahi anuranjanto, ","tha-ap546:4.2":"loke lokantagu jino; ","tha-ap546:4.3":"Vacanena vibodhento, ","tha-ap546:4.4":"veneyyapadumani so. ","tha-ap546:5.1":"Vesarajjehi sampanno, ","tha-ap546:5.2":"catuhi purisuttamo; ","tha-ap546:5.3":"Pahinabhayasarajjo, ","tha-ap546:5.4":"khemappatto visarado. ","tha-ap546:6.1":"Asabham pavaram thanam, ","tha-ap546:6.2":"buddhabhuminca kevalam; ","tha-ap546:6.3":"Patijanati lokaggo, ","tha-ap546:6.4":"natthi sancodako kvaci. ","tha-ap546:7.1":"Sihanadamasambhitam, ","tha-ap546:7.2":"nadato tassa tadino; ","tha-ap546:7.3":"Devo naro va brahma va, ","tha-ap546:7.4":"pativatta na vijjati. ","tha-ap546:8.1":"Desento pavaram dhammam, ","tha-ap546:8.2":"santarento sadevakam; ","tha-ap546:8.3":"Dhammacakkam pavatteti, ","tha-ap546:8.4":"parisasu visarado. ","tha-ap546:9.1":"Patibhanavatam aggam, ","tha-ap546:9.2":"savakam sadhusammatam; ","tha-ap546:9.3":"Gunam bahum pakittetva, ","tha-ap546:9.4":"etadagge thapesi tam. ","tha-ap546:10.1":"Tadaham hamsavatiyam, ","tha-ap546:10.2":"brahmano sadhusammato; ","tha-ap546:10.3":"Sabbavedavidu jato, ","tha-ap546:10.4":"vagiso vadisudano. ","tha-ap546:11.1":"Upecca tam mahaviram, ","tha-ap546:11.2":"sutvaham dhammadesanam; ","tha-ap546:11.3":"Pitivaram patilabhim, ","tha-ap546:11.4":"savakassa gune rato. ","tha-ap546:12.1":"Nimantetvava sugatam, ","tha-ap546:12.2":"sasangham lokanandanam; ","tha-ap546:12.3":"Sattaham bhojayitvaham, ","tha-ap546:12.4":"dussehacchadayim tada. ","tha-ap546:13.1":"Nipacca sirasa pade, ","tha-ap546:13.2":"katokaso katanjali; ","tha-ap546:13.3":"Ekamantam thito hattho, ","tha-ap546:13.4":"santhavim jinamuttamam. ","tha-ap546:14.1":"‘Namo te vadimaddana, ","tha-ap546:14.2":"namo te isisattama; ","tha-ap546:14.3":"Namo te sabbalokagga, ","tha-ap546:14.4":"namo te abhayam kara. ","tha-ap546:15.1":"Namo te maramathana, ","tha-ap546:15.2":"namo te ditthisudana; ","tha-ap546:15.3":"Namo te santisukhada, ","tha-ap546:15.4":"namo te saranam kara. ","tha-ap546:16.1":"Anathanam bhavam natho, ","tha-ap546:16.2":"bhitanam abhayappado; ","tha-ap546:16.3":"Vissamabhumi santanam, ","tha-ap546:16.4":"saranam saranesinam’. ","tha-ap546:17.1":"Evamadihi sambuddham, ","tha-ap546:17.2":"santhavitva mahagunam; ","tha-ap546:17.3":"Avocam vadisudassa, ","tha-ap546:17.4":"gatim pappomi bhikkhuno. ","tha-ap546:18.1":"Tada avoca bhagava, ","tha-ap546:18.2":"anantapatibhanava; ","tha-ap546:18.3":"‘Yo so buddham abhojesi, ","tha-ap546:18.4":"sattaham sahasavakam. ","tha-ap546:19.1":"Gunanca me pakittesi, ","tha-ap546:19.2":"pasanno sehi panibhi; ","tha-ap546:19.3":"Eso patthayate thanam, ","tha-ap546:19.4":"vadisudassa bhikkhuno. ","tha-ap546:20.1":"Anagatamhi addhane, ","tha-ap546:20.2":"lacchase tam manoratham; ","tha-ap546:20.3":"Devamanusasampattim, ","tha-ap546:20.4":"anubhotva anappakam. ","tha-ap546:21.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap546:21.2":"okkakakulasambhavo; ","tha-ap546:21.3":"Gotamo nama gottena, ","tha-ap546:21.4":"sattha loke bhavissati. ","tha-ap546:22.1":"Tassa dhammesu dayado, ","tha-ap546:22.2":"oraso dhammanimmito; ","tha-ap546:22.3":"Vangiso nama namena, ","tha-ap546:22.4":"hessati satthu savako’. ","tha-ap546:23.1":"Tam sutva mudito hutva, ","tha-ap546:23.2":"yavajivam tada jinam; ","tha-ap546:23.3":"Paccayehi upatthasim, ","tha-ap546:23.4":"mettacitto tathagatam. ","tha-ap546:24.1":"Tena kammena sukatena, ","tha-ap546:24.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","tha-ap546:24.3":"Jahitva manusam deham, ","tha-ap546:24.4":"tusitam agamasaham. ","tha-ap546:25.1":"Pacchime ca bhave dani, ","tha-ap546:25.2":"jato vippakule aham; ","tha-ap546:25.3":"Paccajato yada asim, ","tha-ap546:25.4":"jatiya sattavassiko. ","tha-ap546:26.1":"Sabbavedavidu jato, ","tha-ap546:26.2":"vadasatthavisarado; ","tha-ap546:26.3":"Vadissaro cittakathi, ","tha-ap546:26.4":"paravadappamaddano. ","tha-ap546:27.1":"Vange jatoti vangiso, ","tha-ap546:27.2":"vacane issaroti va; ","tha-ap546:27.3":"Vangiso iti me namam, ","tha-ap546:27.4":"abhavi lokasammatam. ","tha-ap546:28.1":"Yadaham vinnutam patto, ","tha-ap546:28.2":"thito pathamayobbane; ","tha-ap546:28.3":"Tada rajagahe ramme, ","tha-ap546:28.4":"sariputtamahaddasam. ","tha-ap546:29.1":"Pancavisatimam bhanavaram. ","tha-ap546:30.1":"Pindaya vicarantam tam, ","tha-ap546:30.2":"pattapanim susamvutam; ","tha-ap546:30.3":"Alolakkhim mitabhanim, ","tha-ap546:30.4":"yugamattam nidakkhitam. ","tha-ap546:31.1":"Tam disva vimhito hutva, ","tha-ap546:31.2":"avocam mamanucchavam; ","tha-ap546:31.3":"Kanikaramva nicitam, ","tha-ap546:31.4":"cittam gathapadam aham. ","tha-ap546:32.1":"Acikkhi so me sattharam, ","tha-ap546:32.2":"sambuddham lokanayakam; ","tha-ap546:32.3":"Tada so pandito viro, ","tha-ap546:32.4":"uttarim samavoca me. ","tha-ap546:33.1":"Viragasamhitam vakyam, ","tha-ap546:33.2":"katva duddasamuttamam; ","tha-ap546:33.3":"Vicittapatibhanehi, ","tha-ap546:33.4":"tosito tena tadina. ","tha-ap546:34.1":"Nipacca sirasa pade, ","tha-ap546:34.2":"‘pabbajehi’ti mam bravi; ","tha-ap546:34.3":"Tato mam sa mahapanno, ","tha-ap546:34.4":"buddhasetthamupanayi. ","tha-ap546:35.1":"Nipacca sirasa pade, ","tha-ap546:35.2":"nisidim satthu santike; ","tha-ap546:35.3":"Mamaha vadatam settho, ","tha-ap546:35.4":"‘kacci vangisa janasi’. ","tha-ap546:36.1":"Kinci sippanti tassaham, ","tha-ap546:36.2":"‘janami’ti ca abravim; ","tha-ap546:36.3":"‘Matasisam vanacchuddham, ","tha-ap546:36.4":"api barasavassikam; ","tha-ap546:36.5":"Tava vijjavisesena, ","tha-ap546:36.6":"sace sakkosi vacaya’. ","tha-ap546:37.1":"‘Amoti me patinnate, ","tha-ap546:37.2":"tini sisani dassayi; ","tha-ap546:37.3":"Nirayanaradevesu, ","tha-ap546:37.4":"upapanne avacayim’. ","tha-ap546:38.1":"Tada khinasavasseva, ","tha-ap546:38.2":"sisam dassesi nayako; ","tha-ap546:38.3":"Tatoham vihatarambho, ","tha-ap546:38.4":"pabbajjam samayacisam. ","tha-ap546:39.1":"Pabbajitvana sugatam, ","tha-ap546:39.2":"santhavami tahim tahim; ","tha-ap546:39.3":"Tato mam kabbavittosi, ","tha-ap546:39.4":"ujjhayantiha bhikkhavo. ","tha-ap546:40.1":"Tato vimamsanattham me, ","tha-ap546:40.2":"aha buddho vinayako; ","tha-ap546:40.3":"‘Takkika panima gatha, ","tha-ap546:40.4":"thanaso patibhanti tam’. ","tha-ap546:41.1":"‘Na kabbavittoham vira, ","tha-ap546:41.2":"thanaso patibhanti mam’; ","tha-ap546:41.3":"‘Tena hi dani vangisa, ","tha-ap546:41.4":"thanaso santhavahi mam’. ","tha-ap546:42.1":"Tadaham santhavim viram, ","tha-ap546:42.2":"gathahi isisattamam; ","tha-ap546:42.3":"Thanaso me tada tuttho, ","tha-ap546:42.4":"jino agge thapesi mam. ","tha-ap546:43.1":"Patibhanena cittena, ","tha-ap546:43.2":"annesamatimannaham; ","tha-ap546:43.3":"Pesale tena samviggo, ","tha-ap546:43.4":"arahattamapapunim. ","tha-ap546:44.1":"‘Patibhanavatam aggo, ","tha-ap546:44.2":"anno koci na vijjati; ","tha-ap546:44.3":"Yathayam bhikkhu vangiso, ","tha-ap546:44.4":"evam dharetha bhikkhavo’. ","tha-ap546:45.1":"Satasahasse katam kammam, ","tha-ap546:45.2":"phalam dassesi me idha; ","tha-ap546:45.3":"Sumutto saravegova, ","tha-ap546:45.4":"kilese jhapayim mama. ","tha-ap546:46.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap546:46.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap546:46.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap546:47.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap546:47.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap546:47.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap546:48.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap546:48.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap546:48.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap546:49.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma vangiso thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap546:50.1":"Vangisattherassapadanam catuttham. "}